c: 39
v: 10
t: "Vuga uti \"Yemwe bagaragu banjye bemeye! Nimutinye Nyagasani wanyu; babandi bakoze neza kuri iyi si bazagororerwa ibyiza (Ijuru). Kandi isi ya Allah ni ngari (niba aho muri bitaborohera gusenga Allah, nimwimukire ahandi). Mu by’ukuri, abihangana bazagororerwa ibihembo byabo byuzuye, nta kubara"